			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "* Don't recruit Shadowheart\r\n* Start Protection from the Voice of the Absolute event by entering Goblin Camp (or try to leave to Act2/Act1B\r\n* When Shadowheart appears, don't recruit her and either:\r\nA) Left to Act2/Act1B\r\nB) Start a fight with her in the dialog, run away without killing her and take a Long Rest.\r\n* Return to the place you've seen her and approach her dead body."
				},
