				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The party comments on seeing Shadowheart dead somehow (she was killed by the Orpheus artefact, which then teleported to the player's campsite). They remark with surprise on seeing her. If they subsequently use Speak with Dead, they receive a hint as to what happened to her."
				}
